for any java class if you allow to create only one object such type of class is called Singleton class
Example : runtime businessdeligate servicelotor etc
Advanced of Singleton class
what is the need of Sngleton object?
performance and memory utilise is the main reson for Singleton
Here run time a sob object akta object ar memory share kore thake
if several pepople have same requriment then it is not
requirement to create a seprate object for every requirement
.
